vote.title: Authorize a twelve-month funding agreement with the Dallas Arboretum and Botanical Society, Inc. in the amount of $374,393.00 to provide services and program support within the city of Dallas for the period of October 1, 2020 through September 30, 2021 - Not to exceed $374,393.00 - Financing: General Fund
